  "caption": "₹500 tee, zero margin left? Wrong printing method. 🧮\n\nBlank costs ₹140. Screen print adds ₹25-30 (margin: ₹300). DTF adds ₹45-50 (margin: ₹280). Embroidery adds ₹60-70 (margin: ₹250).\n\nMonsoon? DTF wins—no air-dry delays. Screen print doubles drying time in humidity.\n\nSave this post before your next bulk order 👇",
